00:51:13.500 --> 00:51:14.500
Papa !

769
00:51:14.600 --> 00:51:15.500
Mon fils !

770
00:51:15.600 --> 00:51:18.500
Talkie-walkies !

771
00:51:18.600 --> 00:51:19.600
Talkie-walkies !

772
